      "content": "but that's just the thing... i don't want to be a \"strength\" to them. i want to be a benefit. right now, i'm just a subtraction. if i'm gone, the math changes. the money they'd save, the stress that vanishes... it feels like the only way to actually do something good for them is to stop being a part of the equation. doesn't that just make sense?",
